<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Choix du paiement</title>
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
		<style>
			body,
			html {
				height: 100%;
			}
			.centered-content {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				height: 90vh;
			}
			.payment-button {
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				justify-content: center;
				align-items: center;
				padding: 20px;
				width: 150px;
				height: 200px;
				text-decoration: none;
				color: inherit;
			}
			.payment-button img {
				max-width: 100px;
				max-height: 100px;
				margin-bottom: 15px;
			}
			.disabled-link {
				pointer-events: none; /* Empêche les interactions */
				color: gray; /* Apparence grisée */
				cursor: not-allowed;
				opacity: 0.5;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>

		<div class="row text-center pt-5">
			<h2>CHOISISSEZ VOTRE MOYEN DE PAIEMENT</h2>
			<h5 class="text-xl text-center font-normal mb-5 pt-5 p-5">
				En cas de
				<strong class="text-pink-500">difficultés</strong>
				à booker votre rendez-vous sur le site, consultez les disponibilités,<br>
				choisissez le créneau voulu et contactez nous
				<strong>
					<a class="text-pink-500 underline" href="https://wa.me/22997853512">ICI</a>
				</strong>
				pour confirmer votre rendez-vous.
			</h5>
		</div>

		<div class="centered-content">
			<div class="row text-center">
				<div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Choix du paiement">
					<a href="{{ path('payment_init', { rendezvou: rendezvous.id }) }}" class="col btn payment-button border border-2">
						<img src="../assets/feda-logo.svg" alt="Fedapay">
						<span>Fedapay</span>
					</a>
					<a href="{{ path('feexpay_form', { rendezvou: rendezvous.id }) }}" class="col btn payment-button border border-2 ms-3">
						<img src="../assets/feexpay-logo.png" alt="Feexpay">
						<span>Feexpay</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	</body>
</html>
